snippet.title: Johnny Depp's lawyer BLASTS Amber Heard & her team out the water!! (Heard, Whitney)
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's lawyer BLASTS Amber & her team out the water!! (Heard, Whitney)

Adam Waldman is Johnny Depp's lawyer and is just doing a fantastic job of setting everyone on the case straight!!

Hello and welcome to Come Geek Some! For all things Geek, like and subscribe to the channel!
